[t5].[PictureId], [t5].[TechnicalDocumentId], [t5].[TechnicalPropertyId], [t5].[ThumbImageId], [t5].[Title], [t5].[Types], [t5].[data_class]
FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentPageId], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypesId], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsBayi], [c0].[IsBireysel], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[IsEndustri], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsGallery], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsInteral], [c0].[IsInterax], [c0].[IsIntersecure], [c0].[IsInterwall], [c0].[IsMap], [c0].[IsMimar], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsStatus], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[LoginCount], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeywords], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[OrjId1], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
    WHERE [c0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [c].[ContentPageId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[ThumbImageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[PictureId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
    WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL

[t4].[TechnicalPropertyId], [t4].[ThumbImageId], [t4].[Title], [t4].[Types], [t4].[data_class], [t5].[Id], [t5].[Alt], [t5].[BIMFileId], [t5].[BannerImageId], [t5].[CadDataId], [t5].[CreaDate], [t5].[PictureId], [t5].[TechnicalDocumentId], [t5].[TechnicalPropertyId], [t5].[ThumbImageId], [t5].[Title], [t5].[Types], [t5].[data_class]
FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentPageId], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypesId], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsBayi], [c0].[IsBireysel], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[IsEndustri], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsGallery], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsInteral], [c0].[IsInterax], [c0].[IsIntersecure], [c0].[IsInterwall], [c0].[IsMap], [c0].[IsMimar], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsStatus], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[LoginCount], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeywords], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[OrjId1], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
    WHERE [c0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [c].[ContentPageId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d]
    WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[ThumbImageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
    WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[PictureId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
    WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d4].[Id], [d4].[Alt], [d4].[BIMFileId], [d4].[BannerImageId], [d4].[CadDataId], [d4].[CreaDate], [d4].[CreaUser], [d4].[DocumentId], [d4].[GalleryId], [d4].[Guid], [d4].[IsDeleted], [d4].[IsStatus], [d4].[Link], [d4].[LoginCount], [d4].[ModDate], [d4].[ModUser], [d4].[Name], [d4].[OrderNo], [d4].[PictureId], [d4].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d4].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d4].[ThumbImageId], [d4].[Title], [d4].[Types], [d4].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d4]
    WHERE [d4].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t3].[Id], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

[CreaUser3], [t2].[DescName], [t2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted3], [t2].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus3], [t2].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount3], [t2].[Mail], [t2].[MailCC], [t2].[ModDate] AS [ModDate3], [t2].[ModUser] AS [ModUser3], [t2].[Name] AS [Name3], [t2].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo3]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

[t].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser0], [t].[DocumentId], [t].[GalleryId], [t].[Guid], [t].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [t].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus0], [t].[Link] AS [Link0], [t].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount0], [t].[ModDate] AS [ModDate0], [t].[ModUser] AS [ModUser0], [t].[Name] AS [Name0], [t].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo0], [t].[PictureId], [t].[TechnicalDocumentId], [t].[TechnicalPropertyId], [t].[ThumbImageId], [t].[Title], [t].[Types], [t].[data_class], [t0].[Id] AS [Id1], [t0].[Alt] AS [Alt0], [t0].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId0], [t0].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId0], [t0].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId0], [t0].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate1], [t0].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser1], [t0].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId0], [t0].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId0], [t0].[Guid] AS [Guid0], [t0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [t0].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus1], [t0].[Link] AS [Link1], [t0].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount1], [t0].[ModDate] AS [ModDate1], [t0].[ModUser] AS [ModUser1], [t0].[Name] AS [Name1], [t0].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo1], [t0].[PictureId] AS [PictureId0], [t0].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId0], [t0].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId0], [t0].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId0], [t0].[Title] AS [Title0], [t0].[Types] AS [Types0], [t0].[data_class] AS [data_class0], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Alt] AS [Alt1], [t1].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId1], [t1].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId1], [t1].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId1], [t1].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate2], [t1].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser2], [t1].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId1], [t1].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId1], [t1].[Guid] AS [Guid1], [t1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted2], [t1].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus2], [t1].[Link] AS [Link2], [t1].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount2], [t1].[ModDate] AS [ModDate2], [t1].[ModUser] AS [ModUser2], [t1].[Name] AS [Name2], [t1].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo2], [t1].[PictureId] AS [PictureId1], [t1].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId1], [t1].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId1], [t1].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId1], [t1].[Title] AS [Title1], [t1].[Types] AS [Types1], [t1].[data_class] AS [data_class1], [t2].[Id] AS [Id3], [t2].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate3], [t2].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser3], [t2].[DescName], [t2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted3], [t2].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus3], [t2].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount3], [t2].[Mail], [t2].[MailCC], [t2].[ModDate] AS [ModDate3], [t2].[ModUser] AS [ModUser3], [t2].[Name] AS [Name3], [t2].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo3]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id], [t3].[Id], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

[t0].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate1], [t0].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser1], [t0].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId0], [t0].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId0], [t0].[Guid] AS [Guid0], [t0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [t0].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus1], [t0].[Link] AS [Link1], [t0].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount1], [t0].[ModDate] AS [ModDate1], [t0].[ModUser] AS [ModUser1], [t0].[Name] AS [Name1], [t0].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo1], [t0].[PictureId] AS [PictureId0], [t0].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId0], [t0].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId0], [t0].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId0], [BannerImageId1], [t1].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId1], [t1].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate2], [t1].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser2], [t1].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId1], [t1].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId1], [t1].[Guid] AS [Guid1], [t1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted2], [t1].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus2], [t1].[Link] AS [Link2], [t1].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount2], [t1].[ModDate] AS [ModDate2], [t1].[ModUser] AS [ModUser2], [t1].[Name] AS [Name2], [t1].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo2], [t1].[PictureId] AS [PictureId1], [t1].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId1], [t1].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId1], [t1].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId1], [t1].[Title] AS [Title1], [t1].[Types] AS [Types1], [t1].[data_class] AS [data_class1], [t2].[Id] AS [Id3], [t2].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate3], [t2].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser3], [t2].[DescName], [t2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted3], [t2].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus3], [t2].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount3], [t2].[Mail], [t2].[MailCC], [t2].[ModDate] AS [ModDate3], [t2].[ModUser] AS [ModUser3], [t2].[Name] AS [Name3], [t2].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo3]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

[c].[IsEndustri], [c].[IsFooterMenu], [c].[IsGallery], [c].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c].[IsHeaderMenu], [c].[IsInteral], [c].[IsInterax], [c].[IsIntersecure], [c].[IsInterwall], [c].[IsMap], [c].[IsMimar], [c].[IsPublish], [c].[IsSideMenu], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[LangId], [c].[Link], [c].[LoginCount], [c].[MetaDescription], [c].[MetaKeywords], [c].[MetaTitle], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[Name], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[OrjId], [c].[OrjId1], [c].[TemplateType], [c].[VideoLink], [t].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Alt], [t].[BIMFileId], [t].[BannerImageId], [t].[CadDataId], [t].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate0], [t].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser0], [t].[DocumentId], [t].[GalleryId], [t].[Guid], [t].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [t].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus0], [t].[Link] AS [Link0], [t].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount0], [t].[ModDate] AS [ModDate0], [t].[ModUser] AS [ModUser0], [t].[Name] AS [Name0], [t].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo0], [t].[PictureId], [t].[TechnicalDocumentId], [t].[TechnicalPropertyId], [t].[ThumbImageId], [t].[Title], [t].[Types], [t].[data_class], [t0].[Id] AS [Id1], [t0].[Alt] AS [Alt0], [t0].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId0], [t0].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId0], [t0].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId0], [t0].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate1], [t0].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser1], [t0].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId0], [t0].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId0], [t0].[Guid] AS [Guid0], [t0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [t0].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus1], [t0].[Link] AS [Link1], [t0].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount1], [t0].[ModDate] AS [ModDate1], [t0].[ModUser] AS [ModUser1], [t0].[Name] AS [Name1], [t0].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo1], [t0].[PictureId] AS [PictureId0], [t0].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId0], [t0].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId0], [t0].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId0], [t0].[Title] AS [Title0], [t0].[Types] AS [Types0], [t0].[data_class] AS [data_class0], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Alt] AS [Alt1], [t1].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId1], [t1].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId1], [t1].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId1], [t1].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate2], [t1].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser2], [t1].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId1], [t1].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId1], [t1].[Guid] AS [Guid1], [t1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted2], [t1].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus2], [t1].[Link] AS [Link2], [t1].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount2], [t1].[ModDate] AS [ModDate2], [t1].[ModUser] AS [ModUser2], [t1].[Name] AS [Name2], [t1].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo2], [t1].[PictureId] AS [PictureId1], [t1].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId1], [t1].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId1], [t1].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId1], [t1].[Title] AS [Title1], [t1].[Types] AS [Types1], [t1].[data_class] AS [data_class1], [t2].[Id] AS [Id3], [t2].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate3], [t2].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser3], [t2].[DescName], [t2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted3], [t2].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus3], [t2].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount3], [t2].[Mail], [t2].[MailCC], [t2].[ModDate] AS [ModDate3], [t2].[ModUser] AS [ModUser3], [t2].[Name] AS [Name3], [t2].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo3]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

[t0].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate1], [t0].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser1], [t0].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId0], [t0].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId0], [t0].[Guid] AS [Guid0], [t0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [t0].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus1], [t0].[Link] AS [Link1], [t0].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount1], [t0].[ModDate] AS [ModDate1], [t0].[ModUser] AS [ModUser1], [t0].[Name] AS [Name1], [t0].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo1], [t0].[PictureId] AS [PictureId0], [t0].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId0], [t0].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId0], [t0].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId0], [t0].[Title] AS [Title0], [t0].[Types] AS [Types0], [t0].[data_class] AS [data_class0], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Alt] AS [Alt1], [t1].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId1], [t1].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId1], [t1].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId1], [t1].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate2], [t1].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser2], [t1].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId1], [t1].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId1], [t1].[Guid] AS [Guid1], [t1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted2], [t1].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus2], [t1].[Link] AS [Link2], [t1].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount2], [t1].[ModDate] AS [ModDate2], [t1].[ModUser] AS [ModUser2], [t1].[Name] AS [Name2], [t1].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo2], [t1].[PictureId] AS [PictureId1], [t1].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId1], [t1].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId1], [t1].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId1], [t1].[Title] AS [Title1], [t1].[Types] AS [Types1], [t1].[data_class] AS [data_class1], [t2].[Id] AS [Id3], [t2].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate3], [t2].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser3], [t2].[DescName], [t2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted3], [t2].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus3], [t2].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount3], [t2].[Mail], [t2].[MailCC], [t2].[ModDate] AS [ModDate3], [t2].[ModUser] AS [ModUser3], [t2].[Name] AS [Name3], [t2].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo3]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

) AS [t5] ON [c].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]

FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[BannerButtonText], [c0].[BannerText], [c0].[ButtonLink], [c0].[ButtonText], [c0].[ContentData], [c0].[ContentOrderNo], [c0].[ContentPageId], [c0].[ContentShort], [c0].[ContentTypesId], [c0].[CreaDate], [c0].[CreaUser], [c0].[Description], [c0].[ExternalLink], [c0].[FormTypeId], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[IsBayi], [c0].[IsBireysel], [c0].[IsClick], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[IsEndustri], [c0].[IsFooterMenu], [c0].[IsGallery], [c0].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c0].[IsHeaderMenu], [c0].[IsInteral], [c0].[IsInterax], [c0].[IsIntersecure], [c0].[IsInterwall], [c0].[IsMap], [c0].[IsMimar], [c0].[IsPublish], [c0].[IsSideMenu], [c0].[IsStatus], [c0].[LangId], [c0].[Link], [c0].[LoginCount], [c0].[MetaDescription], [c0].[MetaKeywords], [c0].[MetaTitle], [c0].[ModDate], [c0].[ModUser], [c0].[Name], [c0].[OrderNo], [c0].[OrjId], [c0].[OrjId1], [c0].[TemplateType], [c0].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c0]
    WHERE [c0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL

    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL

    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

[c].[IsEndustri], [c].[IsFooterMenu], [c].[IsGallery], [c].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c].[IsHeaderMenu], [c].[IsInteral], [c].[IsInterax], [c].[IsIntersecure], [c].[IsInterwall], [c].[IsMap], [c].[IsMimar], [c].[IsPublish], [c].[IsSideMenu], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[LangId], [c].[Link], [c].[LoginCount], [c].[MetaDescription], [c].[MetaKeywords], [c].[MetaTitle], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[Name], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[OrjId], [c].[OrjId1], [c].[TemplateType], [c].[VideoLink], [t].[Id] AS [Id0], [t].[Alt], [t].[BIMFileId], [t].[BannerImageId], [t].[CadDataId], [t].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate0], [t].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser0], [t].[DocumentId], [t].[GalleryId], [t].[Guid], [t].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted0], [t].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus0], [t].[Link] AS [Link0], [t].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount0], [t].[ModDate] AS [ModDate0], [t].[ModUser] AS [ModUser0], [t].[Name] AS [Name0], [t].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo0], [t].[PictureId], [t].[TechnicalDocumentId], [t].[TechnicalPropertyId], [t].[ThumbImageId], [t].[Title], [t].[Types], [t].[data_class], [t0].[Id] AS [Id1], [t0].[Alt] AS [Alt0], [t0].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId0], [t0].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId0], [t0].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId0], [t0].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate1], [t0].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser1], [t0].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId0], [t0].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId0], [t0].[Guid] AS [Guid0], [t0].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], [t0].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus1], [t0].[Link] AS [Link1], [t0].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount1], [t0].[ModDate] AS [ModDate1], [t0].[ModUser] AS [ModUser1], [t0].[Name] AS [Name1], [t0].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo1], [t0].[PictureId] AS [PictureId0], [t0].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId0], [t0].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId0], [t0].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId0], [t0].[Title] AS [Title0], [t0].[Types] AS [Types0], [t0].[data_class] AS [data_class0], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Alt] AS [Alt1], [t1].[BIMFileId] AS [BIMFileId1], [t1].[BannerImageId] AS [BannerImageId1], [t1].[CadDataId] AS [CadDataId1], [t1].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate2], [t1].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser2], [t1].[DocumentId] AS [DocumentId1], [t1].[GalleryId] AS [GalleryId1], [t1].[Guid] AS [Guid1], [t1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted2], [t1].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus2], [t1].[Link] AS [Link2], [t1].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount2], [t1].[ModDate] AS [ModDate2], [t1].[ModUser] AS [ModUser2], [t1].[Name] AS [Name2], [t1].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo2], [t1].[PictureId] AS [PictureId1], [t1].[TechnicalDocumentId] AS [TechnicalDocumentId1], [t1].[TechnicalPropertyId] AS [TechnicalPropertyId1], [t1].[ThumbImageId] AS [ThumbImageId1], [t1].[Title] AS [Title1], [t1].[Types] AS [Types1], [t1].[data_class] AS [data_class1], [t2].[Id] AS [Id3], [t2].[CreaDate] AS [CreaDate3], [t2].[CreaUser] AS [CreaUser3], [t2].[DescName], [t2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted3], [t2].[IsStatus] AS [IsStatus3], [t2].[LoginCount] AS [LoginCount3], [t2].[Mail], [t2].[MailCC], [t2].[ModDate] AS [ModDate3], [t2].[ModUser] AS [ModUser3], [t2].[Name] AS [Name3], [t2].[OrderNo] AS [OrderNo3]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Alt], [d].[BIMFileId], [d].[BannerImageId], [d].[CadDataId], [d].[CreaDate], [d].[CreaUser], [d].[DocumentId], [d].[GalleryId], [d].[Guid], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[IsStatus], [d].[Link], [d].[LoginCount], [d].[ModDate], [d].[ModUser], [d].[Name], [d].[OrderNo], [d].[PictureId], [d].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d].[ThumbImageId], [d].[Title], [d].[Types], [d].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d]
        WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

    ) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[ThumbImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[PictureId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [d1].[Id], [d1].[Alt], [d1].[BIMFileId], [d1].[BannerImageId], [d1].[CadDataId], [d1].[CreaDate], [d1].[CreaUser], [d1].[DocumentId], [d1].[GalleryId], [d1].[Guid], [d1].[IsDeleted], [d1].[IsStatus], [d1].[Link], [d1].[LoginCount], [d1].[ModDate], [d1].[ModUser], [d1].[Name], [d1].[OrderNo], [d1].[PictureId], [d1].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d1].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d1].[ThumbImageId], [d1].[Title], [d1].[Types], [d1].[data_class]
        FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
        WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[BannerImageId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreaDate], [f].[CreaUser], [f].[DescName], [f].[IsDeleted], [f].[IsStatus], [f].[LoginCount], [f].[Mail], [f].[MailCC], [f].[ModDate], [f].[ModUser], [f].[Name], [f].[OrderNo]
        FROM [FormType] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
    ) AS [t2] ON [c].[FormTypeId] = [t2].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ((([c].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([c].[IsPublish] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (LOWER([c].[Link]) = @__ToLower_0))
) AS [t3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d2].[Id], [d2].[Alt], [d2].[BIMFileId], [d2].[BannerImageId], [d2].[CadDataId], [d2].[CreaDate], [d2].[CreaUser], [d2].[DocumentId], [d2].[GalleryId], [d2].[Guid], [d2].[IsDeleted], [d2].[IsStatus], [d2].[Link], [d2].[LoginCount], [d2].[ModDate], [d2].[ModUser], [d2].[Name], [d2].[OrderNo], [d2].[PictureId], [d2].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d2].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d2].[ThumbImageId], [d2].[Title], [d2].[Types], [d2].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [t3].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [t3].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
ORDER BY [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[Id1], [t3].[Id2], [t3].[Id3], [t4].[Id], [t5].[Id]"

    WHERE [d].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[ThumbImageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[Alt], [d0].[BIMFileId], [d0].[BannerImageId], [d0].[CadDataId], [d0].[CreaDate], [d0].[CreaUser], [d0].[DocumentId], [d0].[GalleryId], [d0].[Guid], [d0].[IsDeleted], [d0].[IsStatus], [d0].[Link], [d0].[LoginCount], [d0].[ModDate], [d0].[ModUser], [d0].[Name], [d0].[OrderNo], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d0].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d0].[ThumbImageId], [d0].[Title], [d0].[Types], [d0].[data_class]

) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[PictureId]

    FROM [Documents] AS [d1]
    WHERE [d1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t2] ON [c].[Id] = [t2].[BannerImageId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[BannerButtonText], [c1].[BannerText], [c1].[ButtonLink], [c1].[ButtonText], [c1].[ContentData], [c1].[ContentOrderNo], [c1].[ContentPageId], [c1].[ContentShort], [c1].[ContentTypesId], [c1].[CreaDate], [c1].[CreaUser], [c1].[Description], [c1].[ExternalLink], [c1].[FormTypeId], [c1].[IsActive], [c1].[IsBayi], [c1].[IsBireysel], [c1].[IsClick], [c1].[IsDeleted], [c1].[IsEndustri], [c1].[IsFooterMenu], [c1].[IsGallery], [c1].[IsHamburgerMenu], [c1].[IsHeaderMenu], [c1].[IsInteral], [c1].[IsInterax], [c1].[IsIntersecure], [c1].[IsInterwall], [c1].[IsMap], [c1].[IsMimar], [c1].[IsPublish], [c1].[IsSideMenu], [c1].[IsStatus], [c1].[LangId], [c1].[Link], [c1].[LoginCount], [c1].[MetaDescription], [c1].[MetaKeywords], [c1].[MetaTitle], [c1].[ModDate], [c1].[ModUser], [c1].[Name], [c1].[OrderNo], [c1].[OrjId], [c1].[OrjId1], [c1].[TemplateType], [c1].[VideoLink]
    FROM [ContentPage] AS [c1]
    WHERE [c1].[IsDeleted] IS NULL

    FROM [Documents] AS [d2]
    WHERE [d2].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t4] ON [c].[Id] = [t4].[GalleryId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d3].[Id], [d3].[Alt], [d3].[BIMFileId], [d3].[BannerImageId], [d3].[CadDataId], [d3].[CreaDate], [d3].[CreaUser], [d3].[DocumentId], [d3].[GalleryId], [d3].[Guid], [d3].[IsDeleted], [d3].[IsStatus], [d3].[Link], [d3].[LoginCount], [d3].[ModDate], [d3].[ModUser], [d3].[Name], [d3].[OrderNo], [d3].[PictureId], [d3].[TechnicalDocumentId], [d3].[TechnicalPropertyId], [d3].[ThumbImageId], [d3].[Title], [d3].[Types], [d3].[data_class]
    FROM [Documents] AS [d3]
    WHERE [d3].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t5] ON [c].[Id] = [t5].[DocumentId]
